Tasty marinated meat to warrant 4 stars.

Returned here for the 2nd time within the week!
Tasty and great value meal. Don't forget to checkout their daily special which is of great value.. in love their double chicken chop daily special....

Good promotion during national day. Portion is gd but the fish is orange breaded and not the normal batter. Mushed potato has a nice mushroom sauce. They have mustard sauce for you to put in the plate as well.

Ordered the ribeye steak at 15.90 and was asked what level of doneness my preferred steak to be.

I asked for medium rare because that's my go-to. Was asked if I was sure, and I confirmed it.

The item I ended up getting was straight up gamey and rubbery with a slimey feel as I chew.

The freshness of the steak is very clearly not there, which I don't expect since I'm ordering steak at a coffeeshop, but this makes the hygiene of the area questionable to me.

Their sides were alright. I like this place for their pasta and other items, but placing an order for a steak was regrettable.

I ended up taking one bite and throwing everything away. It's inedible.
Order double chicken. Crazy portion! 2 huge chunks of chicken. 5 stars for that and Taste is great! But not sure is it becos itâ€™s takeaway, my fries are swimming in oil
